      <img src="/excited.png" alt="Miso looking excited" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 mascot-glow" style="animation: mascotIdle 3s ease-in-out infinite;" />
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black mb-3 text-[#4A3728] dark:text-[#F0E6D8]">Already have a password?</h2>
