        Curious about the philosophy? <a href="/why/" class="text-[#6BBF59] dark:text-[#7DD668] hover:text-[#4A9F3F] underline underline-offset-2 decoration-[#6BBF59]/30 hover:decoration-[#6BBF59] transition-colors font-bold">Read why TofuPass exists</a>
